Notebook[{
Cell["OrthogonalCoordinates", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"a4b23949-171f-4e66-b958-97f3c6d7d297"],

Cell["[LLM Generated]", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"53889302-8d09-4b63-a843-ff87fbb450d3"],

Cell["\<\
OrthogonalCoordinates[g, c, {a1, a2, \[Ellipsis]}, v] returns the Z-valued \
displacement of v on each axis ai through the centre c. \
OrthogonalCoordinates[g, c, {a1, a2, \[Ellipsis]}] returns the Association \
for all vertices. Centre c is a vertex or InfraPoint; each axis ai is an \
InfraSegment, InfraLine, or bare vertex sequence. Option \"SelectCoordinate\" \
controls projection-tie reduction (\"Centered\" (default), Min, Max, Mean, \
Median, All, or a user function).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e8ca3b50-02c1-47de-97b6-f9981554edae"],

Cell["Setup", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"c91da77e-6d91-47f9-8fc3-0efdeee21a6a"],

